"The description of the action that will be displayed as tooltip in the "
"statusbar when selecting the item from the context menu."
msgstr ""
"ລາຍລະອຽດຂອງການກະທຳທີ່ຈະສະແດງເປັນ Tooltip "
"ໃນແຖບສະຖານະເມື່ອເລືອກລາຍການຈາກເມນູລັດ."

#: ../plugins/thunar-uca/thunar-uca-editor.ui.h:6
msgid "_Submenu:"
msgstr "ເມນູຍ່ອຍ(_S):"

#: ../plugins/thunar-uca/thunar-uca-editor.ui.h:7
msgid ""
"The submenu in which the action will be displayed. Leave empty for no menu. "
"Use '/' for nested menus."
msgstr ""
"ເມນູຍ່ອຍທີ່ຈະສະແດງການກະທຳນີ້. ປ່ອຍໃຫ້ວ່າງຖ້າບໍ່ຕ້ອງການເມນູ. ໃຊ້ '/' "
"ສຳລັບເມນູທີ່ຊ້ອນກັນ."

#: ../plugins/thunar-uca/thunar-uca-editor.ui.h:8
msgid "_Command:"
msgstr "ຄຳສັ່ງ(_C):"

#: ../plugins/thunar-uca/thunar-uca-editor.ui.h:10
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The command (including the necessary parameters) to perform the action. See "
"the command parameter legend below for a list of supported parameter "
"variables, which will be substituted when launching the command. When upper-"
"case letters (e.g. %F, %D, %N) are used, the action will be applicable even "
"if more than one item is selected. Else the action will only be applicable "
"if exactly one item is selected."
msgstr ""
"ຄຳສັ່ງ (ລວມທັງພາລາມິເຕີທີ່ຈຳເປັນ) ເພື່ອປະຕິບັດການ. "
"ເບິ່ງຄວາມໝາຍຂອງພາລາມິເຕີຂ້າງລຸ່ມສຳລັບລາຍຊື່ຕົວປ່ຽນທີ່ຮອງຮັບ "
"ເຊິ່ງຈະຖືກແທນທີ່ເມື່ອຮັນຄຳສັ່ງ. ເມື່ອໃຊ້ຕົວອັກສອນພິມໃຫຍ່ (ເຊັ່ນ %F, %D, %N),"
" ການກະທຳຈະໃຊ້ໄດ້ເຖິງແມ່ນວ່າຈະເລືອກຫຼາຍກວ່າໜຶ່ງລາຍການ. ຖ້າບໍ່ດັ່ງນັ້ນ "
"ການກະທຳຈະໃຊ້ໄດ້ເມື່ອເລືອກພຽງລາຍການດຽວເທົ່ານັ້ນ."

#: ../plugins/thunar-uca/thunar-uca-editor.ui.h:11
msgid ""
"Browse the file system to select an application to use for this action."
msgstr "ທ່ອງເບິ່ງລະບົບໄຟລ໌ເພື່ອເລືອກແອັບພລິເຄຊັນທີ່ຈະໃຊ້ສຳລັບການກະທຳນີ້."

#: ../plugins/thunar-uca/thunar-uca-editor.ui.h:12
msgid "Keyboard _Shortcut:"
msgstr "ທາງລັດແປ້ນພິມ(_S):"

#: ../plugins/thunar-uca/thunar-uca-editor.ui.h:13
msgid "The keyboard shortcut for the action."
msgstr "ທາງລັດແປ້ນພິມສຳລັບການກະທຳນີ້."

#: ../plugins/thunar-uca/thunar-uca-editor.ui.h:14
msgid "Clear the keyboard shortcut for this action."
msgstr "ລ້າງທາງລັດແປ້ນພິມສຳລັບການກະທຳນີ້."

#: ../plugins/thunar-uca/thunar-uca-editor.ui.h:15
msgid "Use Startup Notification"
msgstr "ໃຊ້ການແຈ້ງເຕືອນເມື່ອເລີ່ມເຮັດວຽກ"

#: ../plugins/thunar-uca/thunar-uca-editor.ui.h:16
msgid ""
"Enable this option if you want a waiting cursor to be shown while the action"
" is launched. This is also highly recommended if you have focus stealing "
"prevention enabled in your window manager."
msgstr ""
"ເປີດໃຊ້ຕົວເລືອກນີ້ຖ້າທ່ານຕ້ອງການໃຫ້ສະແດງຕົວກະພິບລໍຖ້າໃນຂະນະທີ່ການກະທຳກຳລັງເລີ່ມ."
" "
"ແນະນຳຢ່າງຍິ່ງຖ້າທ່ານເປີດໃຊ້ລະບົບປ້ອງກັນການຍາດໂຟກັສໃນຕົວຈັດການໜ້າຕ່າງຂອງທ່ານ."

#: ../plugins/thunar-uca/thunar-uca-editor.ui.h:17
msgid "_Icon:"
msgstr "ໄອຄອນ(_I):"

#: ../plugins/thunar-uca/thunar-uca-editor.ui.h:19
msgid ""
"Click this button to select an icon file that will be displayed in the "
"context menu in addition to the action name chosen above."
msgstr ""
"ຄລິກປຸ່ມນີ້ເພື່ອເລືອກໄຟລ໌ໄອຄອນທີ່ຈະສະແດງໃນເມນູລັດຄຽງຄູ່ກັບຊື່ການກະທຳທີ່ເລືອກໄວ້ຂ້າງເທິງ."

#: ../plugins/thunar-uca/thunar-uca-editor.ui.h:20
msgid ""
"The following command parameters will be substituted when launching the "
"action:"
msgstr "ພາລາມິເຕີຄຳສັ່ງຕໍ່ໄປນີ້ຈະຖືກແທນທີ່ເມື່ອເລີ່ມການກະທຳ:"

#: ../plugins/thunar-uca/thunar-uca-editor.ui.h:21
msgid "the path to the first selected file or directory"
msgstr "ເສັ້ນທາງໄປຍັງໄຟລ໌ ຫຼື ໄດເຣັກທໍຣີທຳອິດທີ່ເລືອກ"

#: ../plugins/thunar-uca/thunar-uca-editor.ui.h:22
msgid "the paths to all selected files and directories"
msgstr "ເສັ້ນທາງໄປຍັງທຸກໄຟລ໌ ແລະ ໄດເຣັກທໍຣີທີ່ເລືອກ"

#: ../plugins/thunar-uca/thunar-uca-editor.ui.h:24
#, no-c-format
msgid "directory containing the file that is passed in %f"
msgstr "ໄດເຣັກທໍຣີທີ່ບັນຈຸໄຟລ໌ທີ່ສົ່ງມາໃນ %f"

#: ../plugins/thunar-uca/thunar-uca-editor.ui.h:26
#, no-c-format
msgid "directories containing the files that are passed in %F"
msgstr "ໄດເຣັກທໍຣີທີ່ບັນຈຸໄຟລ໌ຕ່າງໆທີ່ສົ່ງມາໃນ %F"

#: ../plugins/thunar-uca/thunar-uca-editor.ui.h:27
msgid "the first selected filename (without path)"
msgstr "ຊື່ໄຟລ໌ທຳອິດທີ່ເລືອກ (ບໍ່ມີເສັ້ນທາງ)"

#: ../plugins/thunar-uca/thunar-uca-editor.ui.h:28
msgid "the selected filenames (without paths)"
msgstr "ຊື່ໄຟລ໌ທີ່ເລືອກ (ບໍ່ມີເສັ້ນທາງ)"

#: ../plugins/thunar-uca/thunar-uca-editor.ui.h:29
msgid "Basic"
msgstr "ພື້ນຖານ"

#: ../plugins/thunar-uca/thunar-uca-editor.ui.h:30
msgid "_File Pattern:"
msgstr "ຮູບແບບໄຟລ໌(_F):"

#: ../plugins/thunar-uca/thunar-uca-editor.ui.h:31
msgid ""
"Enter a list of patterns that will be used to determine whether this action "
"should be displayed for a selected file. If you specify more than one "
"pattern here, the list items must be separated with semicolons (e.g. "
"*.txt;*.doc)."
msgstr ""
"ປ້ອນລາຍຊື່ຮູບແບບທີ່ຈະໃຊ້ກວດສອບວ່າການກະທຳນີ້ຄວນສະແດງສຳລັບໄຟລ໌ທີ່ເລືອກບໍ່. "
"ຖ້າທ່ານລະບຸຫຼາຍກວ່າໜຶ່ງຮູບແບບ, ຕ້ອງແຍກແຕ່ລະລາຍການດ້ວຍເຄື່ອງໝາຍຈ້ຳຈຸດ (;) "
"(ຕົວຢ່າງ: *.txt;*.doc)."

#: ../plugins/thunar-uca/thunar-uca-editor.ui.h:32
msgid "*"
msgstr "*"

#: ../plugins/thunar-uca/thunar-uca-editor.ui.h:33
msgid "_Range (min-max):"
msgstr "ຊ່ວງ (ຕ່ຳສຸດ-ສູງສຸດ)(_R):"

#: ../plugins/thunar-uca/thunar-uca-editor.ui.h:34
msgid ""
"If the command should operate on say two or three files, enter the numerical"
" range 2-3. If there are no limits, this string should be empty."
msgstr ""
"ຖ້າຄຳສັ່ງຄວນເຮັດວຽກກັບໄຟລ໌ 2-3 ໄຟລ໌, ໃຫ້ປ້ອນຊ່ວງຕົວເລກ 2-3. ຖ້າບໍ່ມີການຈຳກັດ"
" ໃຫ້ປ່ອຍວ່າງໄວ້."

